I am not terribly comfortable guaranteeing this behavior.

commit.message:
Ignore dists/ for now

Because of a bug in setuptools (https://github.com/pypa/setuptools/issues/1671),
building our files in `dist/` can cause build failures if dist/ is not
cleaned out between builds, so for now we target dists/.
